svg.aria-label: Graph of a parabola in the x y plane with the origin labeled O. The x axis is labeled Elapsed time, in hours. It ranges from 0 to 16 in increments of 1, with values marked every 2 grid lines. The y axis is labeled Ocean water level, in feet. It ranges from negative 16 to 0 in increments of 1, with values marked every 2 grid lines. Refer to long description.
